data.description: Welcome home to 4209 Prestwick Pl Spring Hill,TN. Located in the sought after Kings Creek community with swimming pool,side walks, beautiful landscaping throughout, and walking distance to Towhee Club golf course and Bird Song restaurant with fantastic menu options. This 3 story, 3 bedroom,2.5 bathroom town home is well kept and move in ready! This unit offers open concept on the main level with a large living room, dining room,  kitchen with island, and private fenced in back porch area that opens up to a designated 2 car carport. Entire 2nd floor is your owners suite with large bedroom, large bathroom, walk in closet space, and laundry. 3rd floor is 2 big bedrooms with a jack and jill bathroom. This floor plan is perfect for anyones needs and is a must see! Don't miss your opportunity to make this your home! Buyer/buyers agent to verify all pertinent information.
